---
import Head from '../../components/Head.astro';
import '../../styles/fonts.css';
---

<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<Head
			title="Pascale Richard — Ensemble pour NY 2026"
			description="Candidate Renaissance pour les Français de New York, New Jersey et Connecticut. Journaliste, élue, engagée depuis 2016."
			path="/v/7"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<!-- Background image layer -->
		<div class="bg-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
		<div class="bg-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

		<!-- ═══ FLOATING NAV ═══ -->
		<nav class="glass-nav">
			<img src="/assets/logos/RENAISSANCE_logo-complet_blanc.png" alt="Renaissance" class="nav-logo" />
		</nav>

		<!-- ═══ HERO PANEL ═══ -->
		<section class="glass-panel hero-panel">
			<div class="hero-inner">
				<div class="portrait-wrapper">
					<div class="portrait-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
					<img src="/assets/images/pascale.jpg" alt="Pascale Richard" class="portrait" />
				</div>
				<h1>Pascale Richard</h1>
				<p class="role">Conseillère des Français de l'étranger</p>
				<div class="geo">
					<span>New York</span>
					<span class="dot"></span>
					<span>New Jersey</span>
					<span class="dot"></span>
					<span>Connecticut</span>
				</div>

				<div class="divider"></div>

				<p class="quote">&laquo; Le plus satisfaisant est d'aider mes concitoyens. Conseiller des Français de l'étranger est une fonction méconnue, mais les conseillers font un travail important. &raquo;</p>

				<ul class="facts">
					<li><strong>25+ ans</strong> à New York</li>
					<li><strong>Engagée</strong> depuis 2016</li>
					<li><strong>Élue</strong> en 2021</li>
					<li><strong>Suppléante</strong> de R. Lescure</li>
				</ul>

				<div class="buttons">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/pascalevrichard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta">Suivez-nous sur Instagram</a>
					<a href="https://renaissance-fde.fr/portrait-dune-elue-a-votre-service-pascale-richard-new-york/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta ghost">Découvrir Pascale</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ PRIORITIES PANEL ═══ -->
		<section class="glass-panel priorities-panel">
			<div class="panel-inner">
				<p class="section-label">Engagements</p>
				<h2>Trois priorités pour notre communauté</h2>
				<div class="priority-grid">
					<div class="glass-card blue-tint">
						<div class="card-number">01</div>
						<h3>Solidarité</h3>
						<p>Accompagner les Français en difficulté aux États-Unis — personnes âgées isolées, malades, familles touchées par la vie chère. Orienter chacun vers les bons interlocuteurs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="glass-card white-tint">
						<div class="card-number">02</div>
						<h3>Lien &amp; événements</h3>
						<p>Soutenir les associations et événements qui créent du lien — de Bastille Day aux salons de l'éducation bilingue — et rassembler les Français de toute la circonscription.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="glass-card blue-tint">
						<div class="card-number">03</div>
						<h3>Services numériques</h3>
						<p>Accompagner la mise en place de France Consulaire et le vote par Internet. Tenir les Français informés, simplifier les démarches administratives à distance.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ QUOTE PANEL ═══ -->
		<section class="glass-panel quote-panel">
			<div class="panel-inner narrow">
				<div class="divider center"></div>
				<blockquote>
					&laquo; Il y a une résilience des gens qui n'attendent pas tout de leur gouvernement. C'est notre relation à l'État qui doit évoluer. &raquo;
				</blockquote>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ TIMELINE PANEL ═══ -->
		<section class="glass-panel timeline-panel">
			<div class="panel-inner narrow">
				<p class="section-label">Parcours</p>
				<h2>D'une carrière dans les médias à l'engagement politique</h2>
				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">Années 2000</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Installation à New York</h4>
							<p>Carrière de journaliste. Rédactrice en chef de France Amérique. Directrice des événements culturels au Lycée Français de New York.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2016</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Engagement avec En Marche</h4>
							<p>S'engage dès la première heure avec le mouvement d'Emmanuel Macron. Campagne aux côtés de Roland Lescure pour l'Amérique du Nord.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2017</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Suppléante du député Lescure</h4>
							<p>Suppléante pendant la première mandature du député de la 1ère circonscription des Français établis hors de France.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2021</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Élue conseillère des Français de l'étranger</h4>
							<p>Tête de liste En Marche pour NY, NJ, CT et les Bermudes. Élue à l'Assemblée des Français de l'étranger, commission développement durable.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item current">
						<span class="tl-year">2026</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Candidate aux législatives</h4>
							<p>Candidate Renaissance aux élections législatives pour représenter les Français de la circonscription tri-state.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ EVENTS PANEL ═══ -->
		<section class="glass-panel events-panel">
			<div class="panel-inner">
				<p class="section-label">Événements</p>
				<h2>Rencontrons-nous</h2>
				<div class="events-placeholder">
					<p class="coming-soon">À venir</p>
					<p class="events-sub">Le calendrier des événements et rencontres sera bientôt disponible. Suivez-nous sur Instagram pour rester informé.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ CTA PANEL ═══ -->
		<section class="glass-panel cta-panel">
			<div class="panel-inner">
				<h2>Rejoignez le mouvement</h2>
				<p class="cta-sub">Ensemble, construisons l'avenir de notre communauté française aux États-Unis.</p>
				<div class="buttons">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/pascalevrichard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta">Suivez-nous sur Instagram</a>
					<a href="https://renaissance-fde.fr/portrait-dune-elue-a-votre-service-pascale-richard-new-york/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta ghost">Découvrir Pascale</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ FOOTER ═══ -->
		<footer>
			<img src="/assets/logos/RENAISSANCE_monogramme_blanc.png" alt="Renaissance" class="footer-logo" />
			<p>&copy; 2026 Pascale Richard &mdash; Ensemble pour NY 2026</p>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	/* ─── VARIABLES ─── */
	:root {
		--gold: #C9A84C;
		--red: #ED2939;
		--white: #FFFFFF;
		--glass-white: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		--glass-white-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
		--glass-blue: rgba(0, 35, 149, 0.12);
		--glass-blue-border: rgba(100, 140, 255, 0.18);
		--blur: 20px;
		--radius: 20px;
	}

	* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

	html {
		font-family: 'Maax', system-ui, sans-serif;
		color: var(--white);
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
		font-size: 16px;
	}

	body {
		min-height: 100vh;
		position: relative;
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}

	/* ─── FULL-PAGE BLURRED BACKGROUND ─── */
	.bg-image {
		position: fixed;
		inset: 0;
		z-index: 0;
		background: url('/assets/images/pascale.jpg') center top / cover no-repeat;
		filter: blur(12px) saturate(0.7);
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}

	.bg-overlay {
		position: fixed;
		inset: 0;
		z-index: 1;
		background: linear-gradient(
			180deg,
			rgba(0, 15, 60, 0.82) 0%,
			rgba(0, 10, 50, 0.75) 30%,
			rgba(0, 20, 70, 0.80) 60%,
			rgba(0, 10, 40, 0.90) 100%
		);
	}

	/* ─── FLOATING FROSTED NAV ─── */
	.glass-nav {
		position: fixed;
		top: 1rem;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		z-index: 100;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
		backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
		border-radius: 50px;
		padding: 0.75rem 2.5rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.nav-logo {
		height: 20px;
		opacity: 0.85;
	}

	/* ─── GLASS PANEL (shared) ─── */
	.glass-panel {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		padding: 3.5rem 3rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
		backdrop-filter: blur(var(--blur));
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--blur));
		border: 1px solid var(--glass-white-border);
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		box-shadow:
			0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2),
			inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	.panel-inner {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.panel-inner.narrow {
		max-width: 640px;
	}

	/* ─── HERO PANEL ─── */
	.hero-panel {
		margin-top: 5rem;
		text-align: center;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
	}

	.hero-inner {
		max-width: 640px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.portrait-wrapper {
		position: relative;
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.portrait-glow {
		position: absolute;
		inset: -18px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: radial-gradient(
			circle,
			rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.30) 0%,
			rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.10) 50%,
			transparent 70%
		);
		z-index: 0;
		animation: pulse-glow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes pulse-glow {
		0%, 100% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(1); }
		50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.08); }
	}

	.portrait {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		width: 160px;
		height: 160px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		border: 3px solid var(--gold);
		box-shadow:
			0 0 40px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.25),
			0 0 80px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.10);
	}

	.hero-panel h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.08;
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
		color: var(--white);
		text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
	}

	.role {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
	}

	.geo {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.40);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.dot {
		width: 4px;
		height: 4px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--gold);
	}

	.divider {
		width: 50px;
		height: 3px;
		background: var(--gold);
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.divider.center {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.quote {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		max-width: 500px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.facts {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.facts li {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.50);
	}

	.facts strong {
		color: var(--gold);
	}

	/* ─── BUTTONS ─── */
	.buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.cta {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.875rem 2.25rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.25s ease;
		background: var(--red);
		color: var(--white);
		border: none;
	}

	.cta:hover {
		background: #c4212f;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(237, 41, 57, 0.35);
		transform: translateY(-1px);
	}

	.cta.ghost {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		color: var(--white);
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
		backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
	}

	.cta.ghost:hover {
		border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		transform: translateY(-1px);
	}

	/* ─── PRIORITIES PANEL ─── */
	.priorities-panel {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
	}

	.section-label {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--gold);
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.priorities-panel h2,
	.timeline-panel h2,
	.events-panel h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.priority-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	/* ─── INNER GLASS CARDS ─── */
	.glass-card {
		padding: 2.25rem 1.75rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.glass-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
	}

	.glass-card.blue-tint {
		background: rgba(0, 35, 149, 0.15);
		backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		border: 1px solid rgba(100, 140, 255, 0.15);
	}

	.glass-card.white-tint {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
		backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
	}

	.card-number {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--gold);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.glass-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.1875rem;
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.glass-card p {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
	}

	/* ─── QUOTE PANEL ─── */
	.quote-panel {
		text-align: center;
		background: rgba(0, 35, 149, 0.12);
		border-color: var(--glass-blue-border);
	}

	.quote-panel blockquote {
		font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.375rem);
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
	}

	/* ─── TIMELINE PANEL ─── */
	.timeline-panel {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
	}

	.timeline {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 3.5rem;
	}

	.timeline::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0.5625rem;
		top: 0.375rem;
		bottom: 0.375rem;
		width: 2px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
	}

	.tl-item {
		position: relative;
		padding-bottom: 2.75rem;
	}

	.tl-item:last-child {
		padding-bottom: 0;
	}

	.tl-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: -3.5rem;
		top: 0.375rem;
		width: 13px;
		height: 13px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
		transform: translateX(calc(0.5625rem - 50% + 1px));
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.tl-item.current::before {
		background: var(--red);
		border-color: var(--red);
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(237, 41, 57, 0.25);
	}

	.tl-year {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--gold);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
	}

	.tl-content h4 {
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.tl-content p {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
	}

	/* ─── EVENTS PANEL ─── */
	.events-panel {
		background: rgba(0, 35, 149, 0.10);
		border-color: var(--glass-blue-border);
	}

	.events-placeholder {
		text-align: center;
		border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
		max-width: 520px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.coming-soon {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--gold);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.events-sub {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		max-width: 400px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* ─── CTA PANEL ─── */
	.cta-panel {
		text-align: center;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
	}

	.cta-panel h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.cta-sub {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* ─── FOOTER ─── */
	footer {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
	}

	.footer-logo {
		height: 36px;
		width: auto;
		opacity: 0.35;
	}

	/* ─── RESPONSIVE 900px ─── */
	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.glass-panel {
			margin-left: 1rem;
			margin-right: 1rem;
			padding: 3rem 2rem;
		}

		.priority-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			max-width: 480px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}

	/* ─── RESPONSIVE 640px ─── */
	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.glass-nav {
			top: 0.75rem;
			padding: 0.6rem 1.75rem;
		}

		.nav-logo {
			height: 17px;
		}

		.glass-panel {
			margin-left: 0.75rem;
			margin-right: 0.75rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			padding: 2.25rem 1.25rem;
			border-radius: 16px;
		}

		.hero-panel {
			margin-top: 4rem;
		}

		.portrait {
			width: 128px;
			height: 128px;
		}

		.portrait-glow {
			inset: -14px;
		}

		.hero-panel h1 {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
		}

		.role {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.geo {
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}

		.quote {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.facts {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
